This update for tinyxml fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-34194: Fixed reachable assertion may lead to denial of service (bsc#1218040).

notes.text: StringEqual in TiXmlDeclaration::Parse in tinyxmlparser.cpp in TinyXML through 2.6.2 has a reachable assertion (and application exit) via a crafted XML document with a '\0' located after whitespace.
